OL,3,CMan dies after falling off roof
OL,5,FA man has died after falling from a
OL,6,Froof in Thorpe Willoughby, near Selby.
OL,8,FEmergency services were called to a
OL,9,Fhouse on Fordlands just before 10.30am
OL,10,Fon 28 March to reports a man had
OL,11,Ffallen while working on a roof.
OL,13,FTwo air ambulances are understood to
OL,14,Fhave attended.
OL,16,FNorth Yorkshire police said he died at
OL,17,Fthe scene.
OL,19,FThe man's family have been informed
OL,20,Fand are being supported.
